{
  "stem": "6258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at the next stop, a big black woman came and she starts yelling at me and chased me out of there!",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I couldn't understand why she's so angry with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Here I want to show my solidarity with her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But she was right-- I was taking her place, because I was sitting there and she had none.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And therefore-- but then I thought about this tram, streetcars in Krakow, which were divided.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were-- and then one after another, one after another.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then there was that everybody should work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, we already felt very bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "First of all, my brother was, at this time, we already knew that he's in POW camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But the bank disappeared-- National Polish Bank, and savings of my parents with this, and his job, too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And therefore, they were-- and the tenants in our house, they were all poor, they did not have money, so actually this becomes the way down.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we already began then to sell whatever we had left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then my parents were working on some very, well, little jobs, and then they decide that I should learn something and I wanted to make some money, so I went to work in a pharmacy, by a pharmacist who was my parents' friend.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many of our Polish friends wanted to take us all to arrange for this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But somehow, my parents were against it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Number one, they knew that it was in Poland when you helped Jews, or hid Jews, and the German found out, these people were also killed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a death sentence on those people who helped Jews, as well as for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Number two, in order to be easier, we had to be not together.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
